holds with a diabetic focus or senior needs forrester research named acxiom one of the largest database marketing services and technology providers in the world and stated that the company “demonstrated surprising nimbleness in modernizing its offering and arguably leads the industry with its digital solutions” in their january  report “the forrester wave™ us database marketing service providers q   acxiom is a  billionayear company representing more than  percent of the directmarketingservices sector’s  billion in estimated annual sales regulatory and security mattersedit this article may be unbalanced towards certain viewpoints please improve the article by adding information on neglected viewpoints or discuss the issue on the talk page november  electronic privacy information center edit in  the electronic privacy information center filed a complaint before the federal trade commission against acxiom and jetblue airways alleging the companies provided consumer information to torch concepts a company hired by the united states army to determine how information from public and private records might be analyzed to help defend military bases from attack by terrorists and other adversaries according to the complaint acxioms activities constituted unfair and deceptive trade practices as acxiom has publicly represented its belief that individuals should have notice about how information about them is used and have choices about that dissemination and has stated that it does not permit clients to make nonpublic information available to individuals yet acxiom proceeded to sell information to torch concepts without obtaining consent an ability to opt out or furnishing notice to the affected consumerscitation needed the ftc took no action against acxiom which had responded that it had followed its privacy principles and was not deceptive in its business practices torch concepts was acting under contract to the department of defense in their efforts to research ways to improve military base security a company spokesman said our policy clearly states that we provide information products which include financial information social security number and other related information where permitted by law and that this information is provided to government agencies for the purposes of verifying information employment screening and assisting law enforcement security breach edit in  more than  billion customer records were stolen during the transmission of information to and from acxioms clients the information included names addresses and email addresses prosecutors described the  case against the hacker accused of stealing the data as the largest ever invasion and theft of personal data ever tried the stolen data only came to light during an investigation of a separate data theft incident based on their investigation prosecutors said there was no risk of identity theft or harm to individuals based on the breaches they also praised acxiom for being aggressive in pursuing the hackers and cooperating with authorities the positive outcome of this investigation is testament to the strong partnerships we have established with our counterparts at the headquarters and field offices of various organizations from the fbi and department of justice to the internal revenue service and us attorneys office in little rock said k c crowley special agent in charge of secret services little rock field office furthermore i commend acxiom corporation for their cooperation and responsible approach to the situation acxioms quick response in contacting federal investigators after determining there had been a network intrusion should serve as a model for others in similar circumstances the two primary hackers were sentenced to lengthy  years prison terms in popular cultureedit the company is the subject of the vienna teng song the hymn of acxiom from her  album aims privacyedit acxiom provides a way to optout here httpsisappsacxiomcomoptoutoptoutaspx see alsoedit list of companies in the united states list of sp  companies notesedit   acxiom names scott howe ceo  acxiom at fundinguniversecom  acxiomr corporation acquires buckley dement lp acquisition expands acxioms portfolio to provide data and database solutions to health care and pharmaceutical companies november   retrieved jul     acxiom to buy may  speh for  million may   retrieved jul     acxiom opts out of optout wired november   retrieved july     acxiom completes the acquisition of claritas europe press release acxiom corporation january   archived from the original on  retrieved    pi announces us big brother awards winners for  archived august   at the wayback machine  emc and acxiom partner to accelerate development and deployment of gridbased information infrastructure press release acxiom corporation january   archived from the original on  retrieved  emc acquires information grid software from acxiom   acxiom agrees to be acquired by silver lake and valueact capital for  billion press release acxiom corporation may   archived from the original on  retrieved    acxiom names john meyer as new ceo and president press release acxiom corporation january   archived from the original on  retrieved    chantal todé acxiom acquires choicepoints database marketing solutions division direct marketing news   acxiom names jerry gramaglia as interim ceo press release acxiom corporation march   archived from the original on  retrieved    acxiom names former microsoft exec scott howe as ceo  acxiom names former amazon exec warren c jenson cfo  a b acxiom corp at nytimescom  googler phil mui joins acxiom as chief product and engineering officer  acxiom signs agreement to acquire liveramp archived august   at the wayback machine  what you didn’t post facebook may still know        frontlines the persuaders corporation for public broadcasting november   archived from the original on  june  retrieved  but where did all this information come from how did political parties and advocacy g