acxiom corporation type public traded as nasdaq acxm sp  component founded conway arkansas  headquarters conway arkansas united states key people scott howe ceo products personicx abilitec infobase customer information infrastructure cii audience operating system aos revenue  billion usd  number of employees   website wwwacxiomcom acxiom corporation is a marketing technology and services company with offices in the united states europe asia and south america acxiom provides marketing and information management services including multichannel marketing addressable advertising and database management acxiom collects analyzes and passes customer and business information for clients helping them to target advertising campaigns and score leads contents  history  early years and founding  growth of company  recent years  overview and corporate structure  regulatory and security matters  electronic privacy information center   security breach   in popular culture  privacy  see also  notes  references  external links historyedit early years and foundingedit acxiom building in downtown little rock arkansas  founded as demographics in  by charles d ward in conway arkansas acxiom is headquartered in little rock arkansas united states the company has additional us offices in chicago illinois new york new york foster city california and nashville tennessee international offices are located in the united kingdom france germany netherlands poland australia china and brazil services are available to companies in other countries in november  acxiom completed the acquisition of buckley dement lp in may  acxiom made the announcement that it would acquire one of its competitors may  speh growth of companyedit according to wired in  acxiom has a history of making it difficult for consumers to remove themselves from acxioms marketing lists in early  acxiom acquired part of claritas a european data provider in  acxiom acquired digital impact and integrated its digital and online services 