assisting law enforcement security breach edit in  more than  billion customer records were stolen during the transmission of information to and from acxioms clients the information included names addresses and email addresses prosecutors described the  case against the hacker accused of stealing the data as the largest ever invasion and theft of personal data ever tried the stolen data only came to light during an investigation of a separate data theft incident based on their investigation prosecutors said there was no risk of identity theft or harm to individuals based on the breaches they also praised acxiom for being aggressive in pursuing the hackers and cooperating with authorities the positive outcome of this investigation is testament to the strong partnerships we have established with our counterparts at the headquarters and field offices of various organizations from the fbi and department of justice to the internal revenue service and us attorneys office in little rock said k c crowley special agent in charge of secret services little rock field office furthermore i commend acxiom corporation for their cooperation and responsible approach to the situation acxioms quick response in contacting federal investigators after determining there had been a network intrusion should serve as a model for others in similar circumstances the two primary hackers were sentenced to lengthy  years prison terms in popular cultureedit the company is the subject of the vienna teng song the hymn of acxiom from her  album aims privacyedit acxiom provides a way to optout here httpsisappsacxiomcomoptoutoptoutaspx see alsoedit list of companies in the united states list of sp  companies notesedit   acxiom names scott howe ceo  acxiom at fundinguniversecom  acxiomr corporation acquires buckley dement lp acquisition expands acxioms portfolio to provide data and database solutions to health care and pharmaceutical companies november   retrieved jul     acxiom to buy may  speh for  mi